    <title>The services contract</title>
    <para>
        <indexterm><primary>contract</primary><secondary>services</secondary></indexterm>
        In contract-driven development a services contract is specified by the
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem><para>
               service signature with inputs and outputs, 
            </para></listitem>
            <listitem><para>
                class diagrams specifying the data structure requirements for the inputs and outputs,
            </para></listitem>
            <listitem><para>
                pre-conditions,
            </para></listitem>
            <listitem><para>
                post-conditions, and
            </para></listitem>
            <listitem><para>
                quality requirements.
            </para></listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
    </para>
    
